title.rendered: Park Facing Bungalow For Sale In Westend

content.rendered:
A Life Time Opportunity for you to upgrade your living to one of the finest & iconic diplomatic neighborhoods of #SouthDelhi. This corner bungalow is surrounded by parks, thus bringing your family closer to nature, thus making this 800sqyds north-facing house a perfect setting. Though it’s in good living condition with multiple floors, if one wants to have a single-unit house then the #buyer will have to redevelop this property, As per bylaws, the new building can have a basement, stilt car parking plus four floors and a terrace garden. the proposed area will be in tune of 22000sqft. Buying this bungalow can be a great investment opportunity for future generations because of the limited supply & huge demand for such a majestic masterpiece.

Westend has a small club with a brand new swimming pool, gym, party lawn, and gated community offering a secured neighborhood.

♕Asking Price: 75CR
♕800sqyds
♕Old structure
♕ Basement Ground First Second Floor
♕Corner plot
♕Park facing, Rear park
♕North facing
♕Vastu Compliant
♕New permissible area for new building: 22000sqft

Lalit Kaushik

Call On 98183-12077 For Site Visit

http://wa.me/919818312077

Follow @royalerealtorsindia on social media
Checkout Our Other Listings Here
ROYALE REALTORS INDIA

Royale Realtors India – Luxury Real Estate

19 DDA Market, Shanti Niketan, New Delhi, Delhi 110021
